# Bible App Feature Table

| Feature              | Free                                                     | Premium                                                                                  |
|----------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Verse of the Day** | ✅ Daily verse (random or theme-based)                    | ✅ Same, plus **AI-guided reflection** + audio narration                                 |
| **Bible Access**     | ✅ Core translation (KJV)                                | ✅ Extra offline packs (ESV, NIV*, Spanish, Portuguese) + audio                          |
| **Mood Check-In**    | ✅ Emoji-based mood selection (every 4h)                  | ✅ Extra moods (Work Stress, Focus, Relationships) + personalized content                |
| **Quizzes**          | ✅ 1 quiz/day (3–5 Qs)                                   | ✅ Unlimited quizzes + harder “Holier Challenges”                                        |
| **Quiz Rewards**     | ✅ Basic XP + 1–2 badges                                 | ✅ Unlimited XP, badge unlocks, mascots, leaderboards                                    |
| **Streaks**          | ✅ Daily streak tracker                                  | ✅ Mood streaks, family/group streaks, streak recovery “grace passes”                    |
| **Prayer Reminders** | ✅ 1 per day (simple push)                               | ✅ Smart reminders (morning, bedtime, focus-based)                                       |
| **Journaling**       | ✅ 1 basic prompt/day                                    | ✅ Guided prompts, AI summaries, monthly “Reflection Report” (PDF export), cloud sync    |
| **Verse Images**     | ✅ Basic image templates                                 | ✅ Premium template packs (seasonal, artistic, branded)                                  |
| **Meditations**      | ❌ Not included                                          | ✅ Guided meditations (3–10 min, AI-narrated, calming music)                             |
| **Community Features** | ✅ Join 1 plan with friends                            | ✅ Unlimited group challenges, custom family/church leaderboards                         |
| **Kids Mode**        | ❌ Not included                                          | ✅ Unlock bedtime Bible stories + teacher dashboard (Family/Church tier)                 |
| **Institutional Access** | ❌ N/A                                               | ✅ €499/year pack → 100 seats + custom challenges + branded verse images                 |
